review_blob: It starts with a full body and lots of roasty flavor. It ends with a bitter, dry note. Someone took the time to make this beer and I appreciate that. Its not too my liking.
It has some flavor and light body. This might be the session beer Ive been looking for.

beer_brewer_name: Magic Hat Brewing Company (North American Breweries)
review_blob: Its a one-dimensional stout. Initially, ts a little fizzy. Then theres some mild malt flavor. Its not that interesting.
beer_name: Magic Hat Heart Of Darkness Stout (2012-)
